KeysToEntries.1_8_1-01:
Happogahara is a course with a
mix of uphill and downhill sections‥
KeysToEntries.1_8_1-02:
Don't be fooled by the appearance,
be conscious of running at your own rhythm‥
KeysToEntries.1_8_1-03:
I wonder why‥ 
I have certain expectations of you‥
KeysToEntries.1_8_1-04:
Will you become a racer
who defeats Project D‥
KeysToEntries.1_8_1-05:
Or perhaps‥ You'll be a
stepping stone to further their growth‥
KeysToEntries.1_8_1-07:
Ryosuke's reason for keeping
an eye on you becomes clear‥
KeysToEntries.1_8_1-08:
This four-way hairpin has a wide
road width‥ The approach line is free‥
KeysToEntries.1_8_1-09:
Naturally, it becomes a
decisive corner‥ remember that‥
KeysToEntries.1_8_1-10:
Now‥ you should have
grasped the rhythm by now‥
KeysToEntries.1_8_1-11: This is where it gets real‥‼
KeysToEntries.1_8_1-13: Can I stay focuses until the end‥⁉
KeysToEntries.1_8_2-01:
According to Ryosuke, Tōdō Juku
seems to be Sparta's doratech training dojo‥
KeysToEntries.1_8_2-02: I used to be a student there‥
KeysToEntries.1_8_2-03:
My classmate lost to Akina's
Hachi Roku on this mountain pass‥
KeysToEntries.1_8_2-04: He stood out even among the alumni‥
KeysToEntries.1_8_2-06: Why are you on the road again‥
KeysToEntries.1_8_2-09:
Don't be upset‥
We don't know eachother‥
KeysToEntries.1_8_2-10:
Damn‥ I never thought I'd be
able to drive with you on the road again‥
KeysToEntries.1_8_2-13: So fast‥ he truly is exceptional‥
KeysToEntries.1_8_2-14:
The tires are losing
grip due to the first run‥
KeysToEntries.1_8_3-02: Hehe‥ I'm looking forward to this‥
KeysToEntries.1_8_3-03:
I can't keep up with the
rhythm with Sakai behind me‥
KeysToEntries.1_8_3-04: Hey hey‥ I can't stand it‥
KeysToEntries.1_8_3-05:
Don't relax just
because it's practice‥
KeysToEntries.1_8_3-06: Damn‥ Sakai is as brutal as ever‥
KeysToEntries.1_8_3-07:
That guy‥ even when trailing behind
Sakai, the rhythm remains undisturbed‥
KeysToEntries.1_8_3-08: Heh‥ seems like he's quite skilled
KeysToEntries.1_8_3-14:
If I can overtake Sakai,
victory is mine‥‼
KeysToEntries.1_8_3-15:
Too naive, Daiki‥ There's no
way I'll let you get away like this‥
KeysToEntries.1_8_3-17:
Sakai was overtaken‥⁉
What's going on⁉
KeysToEntries.1_8_4-01:
Heh‥ I'll show you the
cunningness of Tōdō Juku‥
KeysToEntries.1_8_4-03:
You've managed to keep up by
grasping my line and timing‥
KeysToEntries.1_8_4-04: But‥ that will be your downfall‼
KeysToEntries.1_8_4-06:
Feinting with the brake lights
 is a routine at Tōdō Juku
KeysToEntries.1_8_4-07:
Just competing in speed cleanly
isn't what battles are about‼
KeysToEntries.1_8_4-08:
Outsmarting the enemy's rhythm is
Tōdō Juku's style of battle‼
KeysToEntries.1_8_4-09: Oh my god‥ they're catching up⁉
KeysToEntries.1_8_4-11:
I'm defeated‥ They took
advantage of my moment‥
KeysToEntries.1_8_4-12: At a point where the front tires lacked traction‥
KeysToEntries.1_8_4-14:
‥I've decided to thoroughly
devote myself to this car.
KeysToEntries.1_8_4-15:
I don't want to loose against
the Integra Type R twice‥‼
KeysToEntries.1_8_4-16:
Don't think you can
get away with this‥‼
KeysToEntries.1_8_4-17: Oh my god‥‼ I can't make the leap‥‼
KeysToEntries.1_8_5-01:
I chose to follow you because
I'm interested in your skills‥
KeysToEntries.1_8_5-03: Let's see how good you are‥‼
KeysToEntries.1_8_5-05:
No wonder Sakai
was caught flat-footed‼
KeysToEntries.1_8_5-06: It's true that I lost to Project D‥
KeysToEntries.1_8_5-07:
But that doesn't
mean it ends there‥
KeysToEntries.1_8_5-08:
Reflect on why you lost‥
and use that to move forward‥
KeysToEntries.1_8_5-09: That is the spirit of Tōdō Juku‥‼
KeysToEntries.1_8_5-11:
I'll widen the
gap just like this‥‼
KeysToEntries.1_8_5-12: There's no way you can keep up‥
KeysToEntries.1_8_5-16:
Apply pressure right at the
edge to create an opportunity‥‼
KeysToEntries.1_8_5-17:
It's worth watching how
much pressure you can endure‼
KeysToEntries.1_8_5-18:
No matter how much pressure is
applied, there's no response‥⁉
